subject: National Invitation Tournament
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: DeNesha Stallworth scored 21 points and Alexis Gray-Lawson added 17 to lead California to a 73-61 victory against Miami in the Women’s National Invitation Tournament championship game in Berkeley, Calif.
